\fIERL_NIF_MSEC\fR\&:
Milliseconds
.TP 2
.B
\fIERL_NIF_USEC\fR\&:
Microseconds
.TP 2
.B
\fIERL_NIF_NSEC\fR\&:
Nanoseconds
