Time unit of \fIval\fR\&\&.
.TP 2
.B
\fIto\fR\&:
Time unit of returned value\&.
.RE
.LP
Returns \fIERL_NIF_TIME_ERROR\fR\& if called with an invalid time unit argument\&.
.LP
See also \fB\fIErlNifTime\fR\&\fR\& and \fB\fIErlNifTimeUnit\fR\&\fR\&\&.
.RE
